    "Ensuring the integrity of contextual information is critical, as inaccurate or manipulated context can lead to erroneous decisions.",
    "IoT systems must implement secure measures to prevent data tampering and unauthorized access [46].",
    "Privacy Challenges.Context Aggregation and Inference.",
    "Aggregating and inferring context from various sources may lead to unintentional disclosure of private information.",
    "CA systems need to strike a balance between context aggregation for improved services and preserving user privacy [47,48]."
